§4. Notation Conventions

- §N.M denotes Section N, Subsection M
- [SRC:name] denotes machine-retrieved source attribution
- {H:id} denotes hypothesis reference by database ID
- {P:id} denotes posit reference by database ID
- Confidence intervals expressed as decimal [0.0, 1.0]
- Temporal references in ISO 8601 format

